*
   * Helper used to define the callback invoked when a message is received for this service.
   * @example
   * myService.on.receive((msg, reply, reject) => {
   *  if (msg.number % 2 === 0)
   *    reply('You send an even number');
   *  else
   *    reject('You send a odd number!');
   * });
   * @return {Object}

